messages.msgSnippet: Mary Ellen, I love that do!!!  My hair is about that short, but I ve never tried that shade of pink.  It s quite cool . Glenda nellebelle
messages.messageBody:
Mary Ellen, I love that 'do!!! My hair is about that short, but I've never tried that shade of pink. It's quite cool <g>.

Glenda

nellebelle <nellebelle@...> wrote:
My dd had a Barbie styling head that she had grown tired of. She asked if she could cut its hair. I posted the results on my blog. Here is the link.

http://melonary.blogspot.com/2005/07/barbie-art.html

Mary Ellen
